# RESTAURANT COMMERCE APP

A modern restaurant commerce platform that allows customers to browse menus, place food orders, and manage checkout seamlessly. This project is built to demonstrate clean architecture, practical features, and real world food ordering workflows.

## Overview

Restaurant Commerce App is designed to replicate how real food ordering platforms work. It focuses on simplicity, speed, and usability for both customers and restaurant operators.

The application covers the full ordering flow, from menu discovery to order placement.

## Core Features

* Browse restaurant menu with categories
* View food details including price and description
* Add and remove items from cart
* Cart summary with total calculation
* Checkout flow
* Responsive user interface

